{"id": "ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE", "rating": 3.9, "userRatingCount": 49, "displayName": {"text": "Madhappy West Hollywood", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOcmVUUlNOMnR4T0VOblRHaDJaM1Y2WVc1RGFGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very kind and their hospitality is unmatched. Jake and Justin are the goat lol. I was able to get what my daughter wanted. I would highly recommend coming here! A strong 10/10 for me. 👍", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very kind and their hospitality is unmatched. Jake and Justin are the goat lol. I was able to get what my daughter wanted. I would highly recommend coming here! A strong 10/10 for me. 👍", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "김정현", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115398799950699714638/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzapFKIrYHWthj0rkWQKygDaxLM6mFv-U0ec1yHs27ODRkxA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T02:45:09.307155865Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOcmVUUlNOMnR4T0VOblRHaDJaM1Y2WVc1RGFGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOcmVUUlNOMnR4T0VOblRHaDJaM1Y2WVc1RGFGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4d90640053:0x19cb5ddde18f3a1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZMm9MczdnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This place is super cute! I love the colors and the styles are pretty simple. The quality is okay, but it’s not the best. Oh, and there’s a cafe inside. I didn’t try the drinks because I had drinks at Community Goods (which are amazing).", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is super cute! I love the colors and the styles are pretty simple. The quality is okay, but it’s not the best. Oh, and there’s a cafe inside. I didn’t try the drinks because I had drinks at Community Goods (which are amazing).", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bruce jk Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117820444488965871044/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxSSidTkelOShU-oZQYKTGNxpqlOAODAyLj471z_XGWakOMJU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-05-03T15:17:02.627889Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZMm9MczdnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZMm9MczdnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4d90640053:0x19cb5ddde18f3a1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSSWIwZFFVV2MwYVdKb1FuUjBhSEp4ZUdkSVVHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sydney & Eric,\n\nJust wanted to take a moment to thank both of you because this brand has dropped a few things that my wife “has to have,” and without fail I can go to you and you make sure my wife and I are taken care of. You are a real bright spot in that store. As someone with over 20 years in retail, it’s refreshing to see amazing customer service in a world where you walk in and most salespeople are on their phones nowadays.\n\nA few months ago, I really wanted to surprise my wife and get her this crop Dodger tee, but it was sold out and I was bummed. Fast forward a few months later, I walked by because I work in the area, and Sydney mentioned that they had restocked a few and was able to get one for my wife.\n\nWith this most recent Dodger drop for the World Series, my wife has been waiting for it since she first heard about it three months ago and really wanted the hoodie. Eric and Sydney worked together and made sure this morning to make my wife’s Friday a little better by ensuring she got the size she wanted.\n\nJust wanted to take a second to spotlight a gems in a world where good people can sometimes be overlooked in such a busy world. So if you do see this, thank you Sydney & Eric.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sydney & Eric,\n\nJust wanted to take a moment to thank both of you because this brand has dropped a few things that my wife “has to have,” and without fail I can go to you and you make sure my wife and I are taken care of. You are a real bright spot in that store. As someone with over 20 years in retail, it’s refreshing to see amazing customer service in a world where you walk in and most salespeople are on their phones nowadays.\n\nA few months ago, I really wanted to surprise my wife and get her this crop Dodger tee, but it was sold out and I was bummed. Fast forward a few months later, I walked by because I work in the area, and Sydney mentioned that they had restocked a few and was able to get one for my wife.\n\nWith this most recent Dodger drop for the World Series, my wife has been waiting for it since she first heard about it three months ago and really wanted the hoodie. Eric and Sydney worked together and made sure this morning to make my wife’s Friday a little better by ensuring she got the size she wanted.\n\nJust wanted to take a second to spotlight a gems in a world where good people can sometimes be overlooked in such a busy world. So if you do see this, thank you Sydney & Eric.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Justin Goodman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101786597013337099109/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzFFNmEGLL2fYFkOGuNP0ZHTWVy1ut6C8Yv65QdkhXpw7Jag=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-27T16:54:01.694082498Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSSWIwZFFVV2MwYVdKb1FuUjBhSEp4ZUdkSVVHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSSWIwZFFVV2MwYVdKb1FuUjBhSEp4ZUdkSVVHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4d90640053:0x19cb5ddde18f3a1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfenFqS3JRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I heard that  there was a coffee shop inside a clothing store through a YouTuber’s video, which made me curious about this brand.\nToday I finally came to check it out. It was ok.\nFYI.\nMadhappy is a standout brand redefining modern streetwear with a focus on positivity and mental health. Their high-quality, comfortable pieces blend minimalist design with thoughtful messaging, making each item more than just clothing. The brand’s commitment to raising awareness and fostering meaningful conversations about mental health sets them apart. Whether you’re after stylish essentials or a brand with purpose, Madhappy delivers both in spades.\nI like this street. It would always be a surprise if you are looking for something chic because celebrity like Justin Bieber also likes to purchase personal items on this street.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I heard that  there was a coffee shop inside a clothing store through a YouTuber’s video, which made me curious about this brand.\nToday I finally came to check it out. It was ok.\nFYI.\nMadhappy is a standout brand redefining modern streetwear with a focus on positivity and mental health. Their high-quality, comfortable pieces blend minimalist design with thoughtful messaging, making each item more than just clothing. The brand’s commitment to raising awareness and fostering meaningful conversations about mental health sets them apart. Whether you’re after stylish essentials or a brand with purpose, Madhappy delivers both in spades.\nI like this street. It would always be a surprise if you are looking for something chic because celebrity like Justin Bieber also likes to purchase personal items on this street.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Aitana Blose", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114305466768852122211/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnIOniuCQgJftrgK9h3rbv2RQuzBmKgGCFNxTAu2PDlssEXhw4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-27T02:02:38.554864495Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfenFqS3JRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfenFqS3JRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf4d90640053:0x19cb5ddde18f3a1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUwBkkE2_woARofMY3t21nAE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGWGRURkJNaTE0V21KS1RVbHdhVEpLYmtjNE9YYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "As a long time fan of the brand and long time online shopper, I decided to come in to purchase a gift in person. Could not tell who was staff and who were customers as groups of people were scattered around store. No one asked if I needed help. Asked for sizes and response felt rushed/uncared for. Dissapointed in the in-store experience, won't be returning.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "As a long time fan of the brand and long time online shopper, I decided to come in to purchase a gift in person. Could not tell who was staff and who were customers as groups of people were scattered around store. No one asked if I needed help. Asked for sizes and response felt rushed/uncared for. Dissapointed in the in-store experience, won't be returning.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marcos Perez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102988447194524045826/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZs-Kymx8zt6q1sAlu2qm7ZI1HcrWmKKe0DpDbnk80u3TY2dxs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-08T03:54:21.919870690Z", "flagContentU